1. *Zločina* su se uveliko počela događati u našoj zemlji. (Crimes have begun to occur in our country.) 
2. Ustanovljeno je da je *zločina* bila organizovana grupa. (It was established that the crime was an organized group.)
3. *Zločinci* su se usuđivali na svoje nesavjesne postupke. (The criminals dared to their irresponsible acts.)
4. Učinili smo sve kako bismo spriječili *zločin*. (We did everything to prevent the crime.) 
5. Policija je brzo reagovala na *zločin*. (The police quickly responded to the crime.) 
6. *Zločinačko* djelovanje je uveliko napredovalo. (Criminal activity has progressed significantly.) 
7. Sud je odlučio da kaže da su *zločinci* krivi. (The court decided to say that the criminals were guilty.)